        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Securing Children in Schools Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Omnibus Crime Control and Safe Streets Act of 1968 to authorize a grant program for state, local, and tribal governments to place and use metal detectors and other screening technologies at schools and on school grounds. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
